<h2 id="editorial-roles">Editorial Roles</h2>

<p>I am a Senior Editor for the <a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/international-journal-of-human-computer-studies/about/editorial-board">International Journal of Human-Computer Studies</a> (IJHCS).</p>

<p>I regularly serve as an Associate Chair for the Understanding People subcommittee at the <a href="https://dl.acm.org/conference/chi">ACM CHI Conference</a> and as a paper committee member for the <a href="https://dl.acm.org/conference/cui">ACM CUI Conference</a>.</p>

<h2 id="organizing-committee-membership">Organizing Committee Membership</h2>

<p>I have served in the following chair roles in conference organizing committees:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>ACM CUI Conference</strong>:
    <ol>
      <li>Hybrid Experience Chair (2023, 2025)</li>
      <li>Student Volunteer Chair (2024)</li>
      <li>Virtual Chair (2021)</li>
      <li>Accessibility Chair (2019)</li>
    </ol>
  </li>
  <li><strong>European Conference on Technology-Enhanced Learning</strong>:
    <ol>
      <li>Workshop Chair (2025)</li>
    </ol>
  </li>
  <li><strong>ACM Automotive User Interfaces Conference</strong>:
    <ol>
      <li>Social Events Chair (2021)</li>
    </ol>
  </li>
</ul>

